{4} Myself, using Audacity audio software to record the shortest time it took between two finger snaps out of four -- which, assuming the speed forwards and backwards across the thumb is equal, is the same time as a full finger snap. Result was 0.544 seconds. 90 minutes × 60 seconds per minute × 500 years / 7,000,000 years = a 0.386 seconds per 90 minutes ratio, so a finger snap is actually an overexaggeration.











